outputs.output_descr: Enabled Eritrea to fullfill its committment in communicating to the UNFCCC, and through this exercise  update its GHG emmission from key sectors, vulnerability assessment and adaptation options of 5 sectors to impacts of climate change, Climate change Mitigation/Adaptation technology assessment and systematic observation and national circumstances.
